h2. Report Bug

If you have found a bug in Watir, you can post it to the Watir General list mentioned above, especially if you aren't sure. If you are sure, you can "post it directly in our bug tracking system, Jira.":http://wiki.openqa.org/display/WTR/FAQ#FAQ-HowtocreateaJiraTicket%3F

